OL,3,C'The car ploughed through people':
OL,4,CWitness describes moment car hit
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,FShop worker Dharma Mundell told ITV
OL,8,FNews Central reporter Phil Brewster
OL,9,Fwhat she saw in the moments after a
OL,10,Fcar "ploughed through pedestrians" in
OL,11,FDerby city centre.
OL,13,FAn eyewitness on the street where a
OL,14,Fcar drove into pedestrians on Saturday
OL,15,Fnight in Derby has described what it
OL,16,Fwas like to see the incident unfold.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
