OL,3,C'The car ploughed through people':
OL,4,CWitness describes moment car hit
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,FIt comes as a 36-year-old man has been
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of attempted
OL,9,Fmurder after a car hit and seriously
OL,10,Finjured seven pedestrians in the Friar
OL,11,FGate part of the city.
OL,13,FThe incident happened at around 9:30pm.
OL,15,FSeven people were taken to hospital
OL,16,Fand two have since been discharged.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
