OL,3,C'The car ploughed through people':
OL,4,CWitness describes moment car hit
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,FDharma Mundell who works at a
OL,8,Fnewsagents metres from where the
OL,9,Fincident happened said, "I was serving
OL,10,Fa customer when I heard a crash and a
OL,11,Fbang sound and then a bunch of ladies
OL,12,Fscreaming.
OL,14,F"There was an ambulance that pulled up
OL,15,Fjust outside my shop and a lady got
OL,16,Fput in a stretcher.
OL,18,F"(She had a) full neck brace on, and
OL,19,Fthere was a bunch of blood dripping
OL,20,Fdown her head.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
