OL,3,C'The car ploughed through people':
OL,4,CWitness describes moment car hit
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,F"There were people all across the
OL,8,Froad, on the ground and on the
OL,9,Fpavement, it was awful.
OL,11,F"When I heard screaming I thought
OL,12,Fmaybe one person was fighting, and
OL,13,Fthen you see seven or eight people on
OL,14,Fthe ground.
OL,16,F"Everyone that was on the floor was
OL,17,Fbeing helped by pedestrians."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
