OL,3,C'The car ploughed through people':
OL,4,CWitness describes moment car hit
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,FCalum Green, who is the assistant
OL,8,Fmanager of the Bishop Blaise pub, said
OL,9,Fthe car went "right up on the curb"
OL,10,Foutside.
OL,12,FMr Green was working on Saturday
OL,13,Fevening but only saw the collision on
OL,14,FCCTV footage, and saw the ambulances
OL,15,Farrive afterwards.
OL,26,@qD@NOUqD@cO]
