OL,3,C'The car ploughed through people':
OL,4,CWitness describes moment car hit
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,FDerby City Council has told ITV News
OL,8,FCentral that traffic prevention
OL,9,Fmeasures will be introduced this
OL,10,Fweekend on the street, as part of
OL,11,Fefforts to prevent an incident like
OL,12,Fthis happening again.
OL,14,FDharma added: "Some people were
OL,15,Fconscious, some people weren't, I saw
OL,16,Fa lot of people with head trauma and
OL,17,Fthere was blood everywhere, it was
OL,18,Fscary.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
