PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774998182
OL,3,C'The car ploughed through people':
OL,4,CWitness describes moment car hit
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,F"I was so shocked to see everything
OL,8,Fthat had happened, you see the
OL,9,Foccasional fight here but it's very
OL,10,Frare that you see that kind of
OL,11,Fcommotion and to see that many people
OL,12,Finjured.
OL,14,F"Staff from local businesses were very
OL,15,Fdistraught too.
OL,17,F"It was traumatic to see, I don't
OL,18,Fthink I'll be going out drinking in
OL,19,FDerby soon which is weird to say
OL,20,Fbecause Derby is usually quite quiet.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
