PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774998182
OL,3,C'The car ploughed through people':
OL,4,CWitness describes moment car hit
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,F"There was bodies up the road so I
OL,8,Fthink the car carried some of the
OL,9,Fpeople."
OL,11,FNadine Peatfield, the leader of Derby
OL,12,FCity Council, spoke at the scene on
OL,13,FMonday and said she was "absolutely
OL,14,Fhorrified" by what had happened.
OL,16,FShe said: "My heart goes out to
OL,17,Feverybody that's been injured in this
OL,18,Fincident and everyone that's witnessed
OL,19,Fit, of course, their friends and loved
OL,20,Fones. It's just horrific."
OL,26,@uD@YOUvD@JO]xD@KOU|D@ZO]
