OL,3,C'The car ploughed through people':
OL,4,CWitness describes moment car hit
OL,5,Cpedestrians
OL,7,FMs Peatfield added: "As an immediate
OL,8,Freassurance to people in our city, we
OL,9,Fwill ensure that over the bank holiday
OL,10,Fweekend no vehicles will be able to
OL,11,Fcome down Friar Gate in those evenings
OL,12,Fwhen people are out celebrating."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
